<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>For My Khushu ❤️</title>

<style>

body{
margin:0;
height:100vh;
display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff758c,#ff7eb3);
font-family:Arial;
color:white;
text-align:center;
overflow:hidden;
padding:20px;
}

h1{
font-size:38px;
}

#message{
font-size:18px;
max-width:600px;
margin-top:20px;
line-height:1.6;
}

button{
margin:10px;
padding:12px 25px;
border:none;
border-radius:25px;
font-size:18px;
background:white;
color:#ff4f81;
cursor:pointer;
}

#noBtn{
position:absolute;
}

.heart{
position:absolute;
color:white;
font-size:20px;
animation:fall 6s linear infinite;
}

@keyframes fall{
0%{transform:translateY(-10vh)}
100%{transform:translateY(110vh)}
}

#final{
display:none;
font-size:30px;
margin-top:40px;
}

</style>

<script>

function createHearts(){
let heart=document.createElement("div");
heart.className="heart";
heart.innerHTML="❤️";
heart.style.left=Math.random()*100+"vw";
heart.style.animationDuration=(3+Math.random()*3)+"s";
document.body.appendChild(heart);
setTimeout(()=>{heart.remove()},6000);
}

setInterval(createHearts,300);

function runAway(){
let btn=document.getElementById("noBtn");
btn.style.top=Math.random()*80+"vh";
btn.style.left=Math.random()*80+"vw";
}

function sayYes(){
document.getElementById("question").style.display="none";
document.getElementById("final").style.display="block";
}

</script>

</head>

<body>

<h1>For My Khushu 🐰❤️</h1>

<div style="font-size:60px">🐰</div>
<div>Khushu</div>

<div id="message">

i love you a lot my khushu i always love you with my all heart i think u have changed me alot in a good way i never want to hurt you and seriously i think u have the preetiest smile in whole world bas kabhi kabar mera gussa sambhale i think i can spend my whole life with you humari ladaiya hoti h i know par joh happiness sirf terse baat karne se milti h yaa tere sath hone se hoti h it stays in my heart forever and i want you be the last one !! Koi kuch bhi bole i think you are the perfect one for me i love every bit of you !! seriously dont ever think to leave me !! Kaise bhi situation hoo!!

</div>

<div id="question" style="margin-top:30px">

<h2>Do you love me? ❤️</h2>

<button onclick="sayYes()">Yes ❤️</button>
<button id="noBtn" onmouseover="runAway()">No 😅</button>

</div>

<div id="final">

💖 I LOVE YOU WITH MY WHOLE HEART 💖

</div>

<audio autoplay loop>
<source src="https://www.soundhelix.com/examples/mp3/SoundHelix-Song-1.mp3">
</audio>

</body>
</html>
